<div class="welcome">
	<div id="home_header" class="col-xs-12">
		<%= image_tag('louise.png', style: 'visibility: hidden; width: 100%; height: auto;') %>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row manifesto">
				<h4 class="text-center">Do you have trouble clearing yourself of your day/thoughts/work? </h4>
				<h4 class="text-center">Are you ready to live with more ease and enjoyment? </h4>
				<h4 class="text-center">Are you open and willing to hear the wisdom of your body?</h4>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="purple-bg moonvibetribe">
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row">
					<h3 class="text-center">meditation &middot; yoga &middot; massage &middot; energy work</h3>

					<div class="entry col-xs-12 col-md-6 text-left">
						<p>I guide people into connection and communication with their bodies, creating a comforting space for growth and healing to occur from within any body. </p>
					</div>

					<div class="entry col-xs-12 col-md-6 text-left">
						<p>Tailoring sessions to meet you exactly where you are and encompass methods specific to you and your unique intentions. 
						<hr />
					</div>
					

					<div class="entry col-xs-12 text-center">
						
						<p><b>MY MASSAGE</b> &middot; Slow-paced connective and soft tissue manipulation to balance and bring you into a state of awareness with your body. Sessions are approximately 90 min.</p>

						<br /><br />
						<h4>one session ......... $125</h4>
						<h4>three sessions ...... $325</h4>

						
						<h3><br /><br />Three month yoga programs</h3>
						<p>Consistency creates a personal practice and a depth of connection of your body/mind. This leads to transformation that happens when one is truly commited to the process. I combine my skills in meditation, yoga, massage and energy work to create sessions that best fit your needs. Sessions are approximately 75 min.</p>
						<br /><br />
						<p><a href="contact.html">Let's set up a free consultation session</a>, if you're ready to try me out.</p>

						<h4>12 sessions ......... $2000</h4>
						<h4>24 sessions ......... $3500</h4>
					</div>

					<div class="entry col-xs-12 text-center button">
						<%= link_to "WORK WITH ME", contact_path, class: "btn btn-default ha-btn" %>
					</div> 
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row text-center testimonials">
				<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
						<!-- Indicators -->
					  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
					  	<% @testimonials.each_with_index do |testimonial, index| %>
					  		<% if index == 0 %>
					        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="<%= index %>" class="active"></li>
					     	<% else %>
									<li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="<%= index %>"></li>
					     	<% end %>
					    <% end %>
					  </ol>

				  <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
				  <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
				  	 <% @testimonials.each_with_index do |testimonial, index| %>

				  	 	<% if index == 0 %>
			          <div class="item active">
			       	<% else %>
								<div class="item">
			       	<% end %>
			          	
			          	<% if testimonial.image.present? %>
			          		<div class="hidden-xs col-sm-3 pic">
			          			<div class="thumbnail">
			           				<%= image_tag(testimonial.image.url(:thumb), class: 'testimonial-img') %>
			           			</div>
			           		</div>
			           		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9">
			           			<h3><%= testimonial.title %></h3>
			          			<%= strip_tags(testimonial.body) %>
			          		</div>
			          	<% else %>
										<div class="col-xs-12">
											<h3><%= testimonial.title %></h3>
			          			<%= strip_tags(testimonial.body) %>
			          		</div>
			          	<% end %>
			          </div>
			      			<% end %>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>	
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="purple-bg">
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<div class="container">
				<p>&nbsp;</p>
				<p>&nbsp;</p>
				<p>&nbsp;</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="container about">
			<div class="row">
				
				<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
					<h4 class="text_center">ABOUT HEATHER</h4>
					<p class="entry">My own journey has ushered me in overcoming anxiety and becoming my true self. I worked for 10 years as a web developer in corporate environments, teaching yoga on the side. I could no longer ignore the pull of my desire to work with the body. I became an LMT (licensed massage therapist) to further my skills in helping nourish and nurture others.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
					<div class="thumbnail">
						<%= image_tag 'heather.png' %>
					</div>
				</div> 

				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<p class="entry"> Teaching yoga since 2012, I have been drawn towards the principles embodied by Ashtanga yoga. Traveling to study in Thailand with Richard Freeman opened my senses to teach focused a slower movement and more internal focus.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="col-xs-12">
					<p class="entry">As I continuously refine my ability to bring myself home, I want to help others find compassion and connection - qualities that are abundant within us all. I believe in the potential for change that is living inside each of us. I understand the loss of hope that occurs when pain (physical, emotional or mental) is present. By bringing a more open awareness to the body, I lead clients into a thriving relationship with their inner selves and their greatest potential.</p>
				</div>
				
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>		

	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<div class="container">
			

				<div class="row text-center insta">
					
					<div class="container">
						<% @insta.take(4).each do |insta| %>
						  <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3">
						    <div class="thumbnail">
						      <a href="<%= insta.link %>" target="_blank">
						      	<%= image_tag insta.images.thumbnail.url %>
						      </a>
						    </div>
						  </div>
						<% end %>
						
					</div>
					<div class="connect">
						<a href="https://www.facebook.com/heather.allmaan" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
						<a href="https://www.instagram.com/ofthefeather/?hl=en" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-instagram" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

